info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.addressing.targeting

Interface Target

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActorPath, Targets

    public interface Target
    Marker interface for all kind of targets that can identify something in Router. Implementations should carefully override default Object.equals(Object) and Object.hashCode() methods, so each target should be an immutable value type.
